title: Open Bar #68 - Ahsoka FINALLY Ends, Robyn Hood Destroyed, The Creator Impresses
description:
The nightmare of Ahsoka is finally over as we review the last episode of the season. Meanwhile, everyone's been mocking the Robin Hood retelling for "modern audiences", and Gareth Edwards' The Creator turned out to be a decent scifi movie. Join me, Robot Head, Reaper, Disparu and MauLer at the bar!

title: Saw X - Bloody Good Fun (Sort Of)
description: I'd be lying if I said I was a big fan of the Saw franchise, but a random offer to watch Saw X gave me a different perspective.
